ISLAMABAD, Mar 16 (APP):Special Assistant to Prime Minister on Information and Broadcasting Dr. Firdous Ashiq Awan on Monday said the government has initiated an awareness campaign with regard to the prevention,symptoms and treatment of the coronavirus.
In a tweet, she said there was no need to be scared of the virus, rather there was a need to combat it with full preparedness and take precautionary measures.
